import React from 'react'
import { Icon, Image, Statistic } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const PeopleInSpace = () => (
    <Statistic.Group>
    <Statistic>
      <Statistic.Value>
        <Image src='./astronaut-moon-icon-vector.png' inline circular />
        42
      </Statistic.Value>
      <Statistic.Label>Humans in Space</Statistic.Label>
    </Statistic>
    </Statistic.Group>
)

export default PeopleInSpace
